text:
Wah... oh, Kogane.
Rushing around is dangerous, you know...!
... Anyway, what's got you rushing around like that?

Costume～～～！
The new clothes got here, right～～?

Hearin' that,
ain't no way I could sit still...!

I see, sorry I didn't let you know in advance.
I was planning to announce it at the next lesson...

There in the storage room at the moment
but I'll go get them real quick.
If that's the case, let me come along too～～!

Eh, no no,
I'll be right back.

Ain't no need to worry 'bout me～～!
C'mon C'mon, let's go～～!!
